page.title: 11ALFABET MANUFACTURING
page.content: The Alfabet Manufacturing company is a firm that packs stationary.It also makes pencil cases which ladies sew.Bought items are wrapped in cellophane for sale.they sell many kinds of things like pens and desk tidies.They also print special names of other companies e.g. GRIFFIN SAVERS OR GREATER MACHESTER MEASEM ----------------------------------- Lye's Industrial History ======================== Joseph folkes was the founder of Lye Forge in 1699.There is not much left of the original forge.Their main products were horse shoes and body armour but also swords and other metal objects.A military gentlemen used his blacksmith for his armour as a modern man uses a tailor for his suits.
